### === 환경 변수 ===
# commerce-api: http://localhost:8080
# pg-simulator: http://localhost:18080 (실제 포트 확인 필요)

### ① 결제 요청 (PENDING 응답 확인)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Test1234!
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451"
}

### ② PG 콜백 수동 전송 - 성공 (PENDING → COMPLETED)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "1",
  "transactionId": "20250816:TR:9577c5",
  "success": true
}

### ③ PG 콜백 수동 전송 - 실패 (PENDING → FAILED)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "1",
  "transactionId": "20250816:TR:9577c5",
  "success": false
}

### ④ 어드민 - 수동 결제 상태 sync (콜백 유실 복구)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api-admin/v1/payments/1/sync
X-Loopers-Ldap: loopers.admin

### ⑤ 중복 결제 시도 (409 Conflict)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Test1234!
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451"
}
